---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ProjectPage from "../../../components/ProjectPage.astro";
---
<Layout title="Modern ISE Website — Bence R." ogDesc="A weekend redesign of software-engineering.ie — industrial style, square buttons, text animations.">
  <ProjectPage
    name="Modern ISE Website"
    date="December 2024"
    tags={["React", "Tailwind CSS"]}
    image="/modern-ise.png"
    imageAlt="Industrial-style redesign of software-engineering.ie"
    github="https://github.com/bencered/modern-ise-website"
    link="https://modern-ise-website.vercel.app/"
  >
    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="section-heading">What?</h2>
      <p>A weekend exercise to step outside my design comfort zone. Honestly speaking, the seed of the idea came from wanting to make a website with square buttons 😅.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:0.75rem">I'm probably most proud of the text animations — refresh the page to see them.</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-top:1.5rem">Why?</h2>
      <p>To practice my design skills, and to propose a potential new design direction for the official site.</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-top:1.5rem">Learnings</h2>
      <p>Design is fun. Square buttons look cool.</p>
    </div>
  </ProjectPage>
</Layout>
